description:
{{sbc|Innate - Wolf:}} Starting at {{sbc|3:15}}, '''Wolf''' periodically selects a {{tip|monster}} camp within the enemy's jungle based on '''Lamb's''' current ''Marks'' for 180 seconds:
* {{sbc|0 :}} {{ui|Rift Scuttler}}
* {{sbc|1 – 3:}} {{ui|Rift Scuttler}}, {{ui|Crimson Raptor}}, {{ui|Gromp}}
* {{sbc|4 – 7:}} {{ui|Ancient Krug}}, {{ui|Blue Sentinel}}, {{ui|Greater Murk Wolf}}, or {{ui|Red Brambleback}}
* {{sbc|8 + :}} {{ui|Rift Herald}} or {{ui|Baron Nashor}}, {{ui|Dragon}} or {{ui|Elder Dragon}}
'''Wolf''' will select another monster camp 40 seconds after killing a marked monster. If an ally kills a hunted jungle monster within 6 seconds of '''Kindred''' damaging it, '''Kindred''' will still acquire the stack.
The marked camp is highlighted on the [[Map (League of Legends)|mini map]] to both teams. ''The mark is removed when the camp is cleared even if '''Kindred''' are not involved.''
